                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Sometimes, even the most ordinary produce vendors experience the most extraordinary things! One time, while traveling back to Fontaine, Eugenie was accosted by a band of Eremites. Her unexpected response: \"Try some fruit!\" Not only were the hungry mercenaries won over by her tasty fruit, but they were inspired to earn an honest living by selling Ajilenakh Nuts in Sumeru...",
